snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach | Exclusive GeForce RTX Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience an all-new terrifying experience powered by GeForce RTX.

This year, Five Nights At Freddy’s fans can sink their teeth into Security Breach, a new mainline game that takes the franchise into the world of high-fidelity graphics for the first time. With a GeForce RTX GPU, you can take those visuals up a notch by enabling ray-traced reflections, global illumination, shadows, ambient occlusion and NVIDIA DLSS, enabling you to enjoy the best possible image quality at higher resolutions and frame rates.

Learn More: 
https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/january-2021-rtx-dlss-game-update
